title: SPY Unveils The Crosstown Collection
description: The new Crosstown Collection is a vintage-inspired, hand-constructed premium collection with beautiful tort and colored acetate in matte and gloss finishes. Unique metal styling details and quality lenses blend fashion and function to keep your style on point—no matter the setting or situation you get yourself into.
